07:24.211 --> 07:26.945
It's really you. Sonny Shine.

07:26.947 --> 07:29.281
Shine... Sheinberg, Louis J.

07:29.283 --> 07:32.951
Sonny Shine is for my fans
of all ages around the world.

07:32.953 --> 07:34.953
It's Christmas Eve, shouldn't you be out

07:34.955 --> 07:37.255
jousting other parents

07:37.257 --> 07:39.424
over the new Tickle Me Humperdonk?

07:39.426 --> 07:41.426
I got mine months ago.

07:41.428 --> 07:43.028
You'd have to be a fool not to see

07:43.030 --> 07:45.061
how those were gonna fly.

07:45.064 --> 07:48.600
My daughter, Hailey,
is your biggest fan.

07:48.602 --> 07:50.669
We once stood in line at 4:00 a.m.

07:50.671 --> 07:52.184
to get tickets to your studio audience.

07:52.186 --> 07:54.425
I think it was the
happiest day of her life.

07:54.428 --> 07:56.775
That tickles my heart.

07:56.777 --> 07:58.944
Nothing means more to me than...

07:58.946 --> 08:00.512
She was kidnapped

08:00.514 --> 08:03.006
four days ago at your Wishtacular.

08:05.551 --> 08:08.092
What a world.

08:08.341 --> 08:10.308
What a world.

08:14.019 --> 08:16.687
- My condolences.
- She wasn't the only one.

08:16.697 --> 08:18.330
Seven other children have gone missing

08:18.332 --> 08:20.765
within the last two weeks.

08:22.002 --> 08:24.102
And what can I do for you?

08:24.104 --> 08:26.404
There's a common thread
to all the kidnappings.

08:26.406 --> 08:28.740
All the children disappeared r...

08:28.742 --> 08:30.942
Around...

08:31.945 --> 08:33.611
You,

08:33.614 --> 08:35.580
your shows or appearances.

08:38.251 --> 08:39.784
And you...

08:39.785 --> 08:41.953
You thought you'd come here

08:41.955 --> 08:46.057
and ruin Sonny Shine's
Christmas by telling me this,

08:46.059 --> 08:48.894
in person.

08:48.896 --> 08:51.596
The police have been ineffectual.

08:51.598 --> 08:53.632
Worthless, really.

08:53.634 --> 08:57.034
But a man as visible, as
prominent as yourself...

08:57.037 --> 08:58.970
You could bring attention to this.

08:58.972 --> 09:01.139
- Resources.
- Resources.

09:01.141 --> 09:03.275
You want money, right?

09:03.277 --> 09:04.976
- Doesn't everybody?
- I...

09:04.978 --> 09:06.980
I want you to help shine a light.

09:06.983 --> 09:08.980
Eww.

09:08.982 --> 09:11.316
God, the letters I get

09:11.318 --> 09:13.886
blaming me for little retard Sally's

09:13.889 --> 09:15.687
pisspoor spelling test.

09:15.689 --> 09:19.324
Blaming me for Billy's sissy boy lisp.

09:19.326 --> 09:21.259
If I wanted to raise children,

09:21.261 --> 09:22.527
I'd...

09:22.529 --> 09:24.763
I don't, I don't know, I'd adopt some,

09:24.765 --> 09:28.233
but I don't wanna raise
your goddamn children.

09:28.235 --> 09:30.669
I wanna entertain them!

09:30.671 --> 09:32.530
Do you see the difference?

09:35.542 --> 09:37.075
Dude.

09:37.077 --> 09:38.214
I'm, I'm...

09:38.217 --> 09:40.011
I've been blending Ghee

09:40.013 --> 09:42.013
and MCT into my coffee,

09:42.015 --> 09:44.716
so I'm totally lit as fuck.

09:44.718 --> 09:46.651
Celebrity problems.

09:48.555 --> 09:50.689
It's not easy, what I do.

09:53.293 --> 09:55.360
Sometimes, I just need a release.

10:04.571 --> 10:07.672
Your breathing, it's very shallow.

10:07.674 --> 10:09.941
You know, it's totally normal,

10:09.943 --> 10:13.878
