get a little lightheaded.

10:17.718 --> 10:21.453
You know, when I was just a little kid,

10:21.455 --> 10:23.321
all I wanted to do was
sit on Dorothy's lap.

10:23.323 --> 10:24.789
I totally get it.

10:24.791 --> 10:26.925
I'd like to go now.

10:26.927 --> 10:29.694
You just, you got here, just...

10:29.696 --> 10:32.063
Please.

10:35.469 --> 10:38.069
For you and...

10:38.071 --> 10:39.871
Hai... it's Hailey.

10:39.873 --> 10:41.973
Hailey, right?

10:41.975 --> 10:45.110
If... no, no...

10:45.112 --> 10:49.481
When she decides to come home.

10:52.986 --> 10:54.419
Thank you.

11:12.873 --> 11:16.207
Don't let her leave the building.

12:29.950 --> 12:32.917
Come on, this way.

12:32.919 --> 12:34.886
Back in there! Come on.

12:35.956 --> 12:39.290
Be careful.

12:39.292 --> 12:42.160
Get out.

12:44.731 --> 12:47.065
I told him

12:47.067 --> 12:48.967
children are bad business.

12:48.969 --> 12:51.236
Messy, obnoxious,

12:51.238 --> 12:52.871
germridden little migraines

12:52.873 --> 12:54.548
not worth the aggravation.

12:55.626 --> 12:58.209
"I have my reasons," he says.

12:58.211 --> 13:01.379
"We all have to answer
to someone," he says.

13:01.381 --> 13:02.480
It's ridiculous,

13:02.482 --> 13:04.634
just a waste of my time.

13:08.922 --> 13:11.623
Did you know that I
can train an adult male

13:11.625 --> 13:14.058
to denounce every God
he's ever worshipped

13:14.060 --> 13:16.594
and squeal on all fours
like a hog to slaughter

13:16.596 --> 13:18.763
in under 24 hours?

13:18.765 --> 13:21.099
Because adults have been socialized

13:21.101 --> 13:22.600
into latent obedience.

13:22.602 --> 13:23.665
But you...

13:23.668 --> 13:25.209
Really enjoy hearing yourself talk,

13:25.212 --> 13:26.771
don't you, Mister?

13:29.376 --> 13:31.576
Well, look who doesn't have a gag.

13:34.181 --> 13:36.114
We located the car
a halfmile from here

13:36.116 --> 13:38.216
wrapped around telephone pole.

13:38.218 --> 13:40.552
It's a total loss,
no sign of any driver.

13:40.554 --> 13:42.921
My God, Mikey.

13:42.923 --> 13:45.023
Right.

13:45.025 --> 13:47.559
About that social media post...

13:47.561 --> 13:49.861
Your son has been dead
for 48 hours, ma'am.

13:49.863 --> 13:51.596
We got a hit and run situation

13:51.598 --> 13:53.313
