14:03.143 --> 14:04.698
Mr. Scaramucci.

14:04.701 --> 14:07.679
Aww, they got you boys
working on Christmas Eve.

14:07.681 --> 14:09.013
That's criminal.

14:09.015 --> 14:11.549
My sister has had

14:11.551 --> 14:14.619
a very difficult morning.

14:14.621 --> 14:17.956
Why don't you officers just run along?

14:17.958 --> 14:20.480
