14:28.568 --> 14:29.801
Where is he?

14:29.803 --> 14:31.469
Go to hell.

14:35.976 --> 14:37.408
Where is he?

14:39.212 --> 14:41.679
You think your guns are
gonna protect you now?

14:41.681 --> 14:44.549
I got something way more dangerous:

14:44.551 --> 14:47.051
A following.

14:47.053 --> 14:50.755
Yeah, 1.3 million,

14:50.757 --> 14:52.857
and I didn't have to buy 'em, baby.

14:52.859 --> 14:54.959
I can't wait for the whole world

14:54.961 --> 14:57.195
to see who you really are, brother.

14:57.197 --> 14:59.938
All right, all right,
have a little dignity.

14:59.941 --> 15:04.269
