excuse for a pecker.

15:15.849 --> 15:18.249
These mugs may fear you,

15:18.251 --> 15:19.684
but I don't,

15:19.686 --> 15:23.087
because I know all the secrets,

15:23.089 --> 15:25.356
and I have all the receipts.

15:25.358 --> 15:27.125
So, you better buy yourself

15:27.127 --> 15:29.360
