15:52.719 --> 15:54.786
Michelangelo!

15:54.788 --> 15:57.555
It's Uncle Blue!

15:57.557 --> 16:00.191
Aww, come on, Mikey.

16:00.193 --> 16:01.993
Come on.

16:01.995 --> 16:03.661
Give me what is mine.

16:03.663 --> 16:06.064
Give me what I deserve,

16:06.066 --> 16:10.501
or mama's gonna get what she deserves.

16:10.503 --> 16:12.837
Don't you think that I won't do it.

17:49.853 --> 17:51.822
Nick?

17:51.825 --> 17:52.951
Yeah?

17:52.953 --> 17:55.586
I'm cold, so cold.

17:55.588 --> 17:57.388
Cuddle me?

17:59.559 --> 18:02.393
