18:02.395 --> 18:04.162
Yeah.

18:08.001 --> 18:11.336
Ssstill cold.

18:11.338 --> 18:13.504
Cuddle me closer?

18:13.506 --> 18:14.906
Wh...

18:14.908 --> 18:16.240
What is it, Nick?

18:16.242 --> 18:17.542
Nothing.

18:17.544 --> 18:20.712
Just, just, seem...

18:20.714 --> 18:21.980
different.

18:21.982 --> 18:24.002
A little glint in your eye,

18:24.005 --> 18:26.539
kinda...

18:26.542 --> 18:29.053
Kinda Mansonesque.

18:29.055 --> 18:30.355
Did you...

18:30.357 --> 18:33.591
My God.

18:33.593 --> 18:35.326
You little scamp.

18:35.328 --> 18:37.595
You killed something, didn't you?

18:37.597 --> 18:38.963
Yeah, you did.

18:38.965 --> 18:40.431
I'd know that look anywhere.

18:40.433 --> 18:42.000
I don't wanna talk about it.

18:44.067 --> 18:47.171
Okay.

18:47.173 --> 18:49.440
All right, all right, look.

18:51.011 --> 18:52.844
Look, what can I tell you, pal?

18:52.846 --> 18:55.446
The first one...

18:55.448 --> 18:57.715
it's always gonna stay with you.

18:57.717 --> 18:59.517
